OL,5, A couple who "ruthlessly" stole tens of
OL,6, thousands of pounds from a children's  
OL,7, football club have been sentenced.     
OL,9,FMichelle, 42, and Simon Marshall, 47,  
OL,10,Fwho helped run the club, used the money
OL,11,Fon shopping trips and holidays abroad. 
OL,13,FMerseyside Police described the couple 
OL,14,Fas "truly despicable," adding the      
OL,15,F"scale of their deceit was staggering".
OL,17,FMichelle Marshall was jailed for 30    
OL,18,Fmonths at Liverpool Crown Court while  
OL,19,FSimon Marshall received a 15-month     
OL,20,Fsentence suspended for 18 months.      
